text: Max Thomas (March 24, 1874 - June 3, 1929) was an American gymnast. He competed in three events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1874 births Category:1929 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
